{
  "id": "adv_bond_kor_01_04",
  "title": "fran4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すず。ちょうど良かったわ\nこれから探しに行くとこだったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ Suzu‚ Fancy seeing you here\nI was going to meet you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "この間、あなたに長瀬麻奈のブルーレイ借りてたでしょ\n観終わったんで返すわ……あ、あとついでにお礼",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before‚ I borrowed Mana Nagase's BD from you\nI've finished watching it‚ so I'll return it… Oh‚ and also‚ thank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ご丁寧にありがとうございます\n麻奈様を讃える同志には、お礼なんて不要ですのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much for your kind words\nBut to the comrades who praises Mana-sama‚ doesn't need a thank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "讃える……同志？？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Praises… comrades??",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、麻奈様の伝説のライブはいかがでした？\nいえ、伝説でないライブなどありませんけれども！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what did you think of Mana-sama's legendary live performance?\nNo‚ there's no live performance that isn't legendary!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "あー……\nまぁ、悪くはなかったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahー…\nWell‚ it wasn't bad",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "（この子、長瀬麻奈のファンみたいだし）\n（さすがにお子様に「普通だった」って言うのもね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This girl‚ seems like a Mana Nagase's fan）\n（It's not right to tell a child that it was 'normal'）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ですわよね？　私のイチオシポイントは\n『First Step』の二番ですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? My top pick is\nThe second verse of \"First Step\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "マイクの調子がおかしくなったにも関わらず\nいつも以上の美声で歌いきった麻奈様……最高ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though her microphone was malfunctioning‚\nMana-sama sang with a more beautiful voice than usual… it's so amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あと、このライブで初披露だった曲が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ the song that was performed for the first time at this live show was…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "（……油断した。この事務所、長瀬麻奈の話が長いのは）\n（{user}さんだけじゃなかったのね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I was careless‚ {user} wasn't the only one in this office who was talking）\n（at length about Mana Nagase）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ラスサビで、麻奈様がこうターンした時に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During the last chorus‚ when Mana-sama did that turn…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　ちょっと待って\nそこの動き、確かこうだったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Wait a minute\nI'm sure that move was like this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ。麻奈様のライブでの振り付けを\n映像を観ただけで、もう全部覚えたんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you already memorized the choreography that Mana-sama showed\nin her live performance just by watching the video!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "いや全部ってほどでもないけど……まぁ、大体は\nだってほら、私ってば天才だから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ not all of them… but‚ mostly\nYou know‚ I'm a genius――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "さすが麻奈様！！\nああ、見る者全ての記憶に残る、あのお美しい姿……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's my Mana-sama!!\nAhh‚ that beautiful figure‚ memorable to all who see it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、私の記憶力がいいだけなんだけど\n……うん、耳に入ってないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's just that I have a good memory\n…Yeah‚ you didn't hear it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "さぁさぁ、こちらに\n一緒に、麻奈様のダンスを語り合いましょう！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ come over here\nLet's talk about Mana-sama's dancing together!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_04-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……余計なことまで言っちゃったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I said too much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}